n's%20Noto%20Peninsula%2C%20swapping%20stories%20with%20the%20chef%20in%20flawless%2C%20real-time%20translation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20frictionless%20conversations%2C%20Banyan%20Group%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasia-hotel-mogul-hospitality-worst-industry-to-be-in-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKwon%20Ping%20Ho%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%2C%20will%20%26quot%3Bopen%20up%20the%20boundaries%20of%20travel%20in%20a%20big%2C%20big%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%2C%20who%20launched%20his%20first%20resort%20on%20an%20abandoned%20tin%20mine%20in%20Phuket%2C%20Thailand%20in%201994%2C%20has%20spent%20over%2030%20years%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry.%20The%2072-year-old%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%2C%20tools%20like%20simultaneous%20translation%20will%20make%20a%20big%20splash%20in%20his%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20AI%20that%20I%20think%20will%20revolutionize%20our%20industry%20and%20travel%20is%20oddly%20enough%2C%20not%20AGI.%20That's%20science%20fiction%20because%20nobody%20can%20imagine%20what%20it's%20really%20going%20to%20lead%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Ho%20said%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20International%20Conference%20on%20Cohesive%20Societies%20held%20in%20Singapore%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAGI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20is%20a%20theoretical%20form%20of%20AI%20that%20is%20capable%20of%20thinking%20and%20reasoning%20like%20humans.%20Experts%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagi-predictions-sam-altman-dario-amodei-geoffrey-hinton-demis-hassabis-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esplit%20on%20when%20exactly%20AGI%20will%20be%20achieved%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20say%20AGI%20will%20be%20ready%20in%20two%20years%2C%20but%20others%20say%20it%20