0very%20new%20employee%20(with%20amnesia).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20lucrative%20corporate%20skills%20these%20days%20is%20effective%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchaptgpt-large-language-model-ai-prompt-engineering-automated-optimizer-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprompting%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20making%20requests%20of%20chatbots%20to%20get%20what%20you%20want%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20not%20as%20easy%20as%20it%20sounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatbots%20are%20like%20children.%20They%20will%20do%20only%20what%20you%20ask%2C%20if%20even%20that%2C%20and%20nothing%20more.%20To%20get%20what%20you%20want%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20explicit%20and%20specific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-anthropic-billions-cloud-revenue-growth-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20offering%20some%20help%20on%20this%20front.%20The%20company%20recently%20published%20a%20%26quot%3BPrompt%20Engineering%20Overview%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20users%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20its%20guide%20applies%20to%20pretty%20much%20any%20chatbot%2C%20it's%20tailored%20to%20its%20own%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cut-pirated-millions-used-books-train-claude-copyright-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20order%20of%20business%2C%20Anthropic%20says%2C%20is%20to%20understand%20exactly%20what%20Claude%20is.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20interacting%20with%20Claude%2C%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20brilliant%20but%20very%20new%20employee%20(with%20amnesia)%20who%20needs%20explicit%20instructions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says%20in%20its%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20to%20have%20a%20rough%20idea%20or%20draft%20of%20your%20question%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20a%20successful%20outcome%20might%20look%20like.%20Anthropic%20also%20offers%20a%20%26quot%3Bprompt%20generator%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20first%20draft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20it%20becomes%20all%20about%20refining%20that%20initial%20prompt.%20Here%20are%20Anthropic's%20top%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20specific%20with%20your%20prompts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaude%20does%20not%20have%20context%20on%20your%20norms%2C%20styles%2C%20guidelines%2C%20or%20preferred%20ways%20of%20working.%20The%20more%20precisely%20you%20explain%20what%20you%20want%2C%20the%20better%20Claude's%20response%20will%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20suggests%20telling%20the%20chatbot%20what%20the%20results%20will%20be%20used%20for%20and%20what%20audience%20it%20is%20meant%20for.%20You%20should%20also%20tell%20Claude%2C%20or%20whatever%20chatbot%20you%20are%20using%2C%20what%20the%20end%20goal%20of%20the%20task%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20you%20can%20organize%20the%20directions%2C%20the%20better.%20Anthropic%20even%20recommends%20laying%20out%20the%20requests%20as%20bullet%20points%20or%20a%20numbered%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20generous%20with%20examples%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExamples%20are%20your%20secret%20weapon%20shortcut%20for%20getting%20Claude%20to%20generate%20exactly%20what%20you%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says.%20%26quot%3BBy%20providing%20a%20few%20well-crafted%20examples%20in%20your%20prompt%2C%20you%20can%20dramatically%20improve%20the%20accuracy%2C%20consistency%2C%20and%20quality%20of%20Claude's%20outputs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20is%20sometimes%20called%20multi-shot%20prompting.%20Anthropic%20says%20that%20giving%20examples%20reduces%20misinterpretation%20and%20enforces%20uniform%20structure%20and%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGive%20the%20chatbot%20space%20to%20think%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiving%20Claude%20space%20to%20think%20can%20dramatically%20improve%20its%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20technique%2C%20known%20as%20chain%20of%20thought%20(CoT)%20prompting%2C%20encourages%20Claude%20to%20break%20down%20problems%20step-by-step%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20accurate%20and%20nuanced%20outputs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20a%20user%20will%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20a%20chatbot%20if%20they%20lay%20out%20the%20chain%20of%20steps%20so%20it%20can%20think%20through%20each%20one%20before%20answering.%20%26quot%3BThis%20thorough%20reasoning%20leads%20to%20a%20more%20confident%20and%20justifiable%20recommendation%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoleplay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20says%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20strategies%20is%20to%20assign%20the%20chatbot%20a%20specific%20role%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Bnews%20editor%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20planner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20technique%2C%20known%20as%20role%20prompting%2C%20is%20the%20most%20powerful%20way%20to%20use%20system%20prompts%20with%20Claude%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20complex%20scenarios%20like%20legal%20analysis%20or%20financial%20modeling%2C%20role%20prompting%20can%20significantly%20boost%20Claude's%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssigning%20roles%20can%20ensure%20you%20get%20exactly%20what%20you%20want.%20Maybe%20you%20want%20the%20brevity%20of%20a%20news%20writer%2C%20or%20maybe%20you%20want%20the%20tone%20of%20an%20academic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReduce%20hallucinations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatbots%20make%20things%20up%2C%20which%20is%20why%20you%20have%20to%20check%20everything%20they%20say.%20But%20there%20are%20some%20simple%20ways%20to%20reduce%20those%20hallucinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthtropic%20says%20the%20best%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20is%20give%20the%20chatbot%20permission%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExplicitly%20give%20Claude%20permission%20to%20admit%20uncertainty.%20This%20simple%20technique%20can%20drastically%20reduce%20false%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20ask%20Claude%20and%20other%20chatbots%20to%20cite%20their%20claims%20with%20sources.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20also%20have%20Claude%20verify%20each%20claim%20by%20finding%20a%20supporting%20quote%20after%20it%20generates%20a%20response.%20If%20it%20can't%20find%20a%20quote%2C%20it%20must%20retract%20the%20claim%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753050596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687d6dc5f748d8c055f5f028%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20released%20a%20guide%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20chatbot%20prompts.%20It%20says%20you%20should%20think%20of%20its%20own%20chatbot%2C%20Claude%2C%20as%20a%20forgetful%20employee.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WW2%20veteran%20and%20TikTok%20star%20'Papa'%20Jake%20Larson%20dies%20aged%20102%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753048157000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F64ba%2Flive%2Fe467e930-65b0-11f0-8dbd-f3d32ebd3327.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc0rvlwxjlj1o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tributes%20are%20being%20paid%20to%20the%20American%20D-Day%20veteran%20and%20social%20media%20star.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%