rer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelephant%20corridors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20have%20started%20being%20wary%20of%20the%20lit-up%20village.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20stray%20in%20anymore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELight%20became%20the%20antidote%20to%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20energy-resilient%20communities%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rains%20would%20bow%20out%20for%20the%20year%2C%20Maharashtra-based%20farmer%20Ambadas%20Bhoye%20would%20proceed%20to%20pack%20his%20bags.%20The%20end%20of%20the%20monsoon%20season%20meant%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20his%20village%20of%20Tulyachapada.%20The%20paucity%20of%20water%20made%20it%20impossible%20to%20irrigate%20the%20land%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%20And%20so%2C%20Ambadas%20would%20migrate%20to%20the%20main%20city%20looking%20for%20work%20that%20would%20help%20him%20eke%20out%20a%20living%20until%20the%20rains%20returned%20once%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20well.%20Ambadas%20earned%20Rs%20215%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20good%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20in%202019%2C%20something%20changed.%20That%20year%2C%20when%20the%20rains%20ebbed%2C%20Ambadas%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sad.%20He%20simply%20went%20to%20his%20field%20and%20turned%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424712%2Fanand-jain-iit-roorkee-alumnus-creates-india-largest-agrivoltaic-solar-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar-powered%20irrigation%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20fields%20of%20groundnut%2C%20%3Cem%3Eokra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lady%20finger)%2C%20pumpkins%2C%20and%20beans%20are%20thriving.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%2