ds%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDavinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad%E2%80%99s%20farm%20from%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%2C%20Baljit%20Kaur%2C%20took%20up%20dairy%20farming%20to%20supplement%20the%20family%20income.%20Together%2C%20they%20saved%20and%20slowly%20expanded%20operations%20to%20ten%20acres%2C%20adding%20tomatoes%20and%20other%20seasonal%20crops%20into%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20goals%20weren%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20daily%20sustenance.%20He%20was%20watching%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20experimenting.%20He%20paid%20attention%20to%20water%20use%2C%20invested%20in%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20and%20studied%20the%20market%20carefully.%20His%20approach%20to%20farming%20was%20never%20passive%3B%20it%20was%20strategic.%20Even%20before%20formal%20training%2C%20he%20believed%20in%20treating%20agriculture%20as%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20turning%20point.%20In%202007%2C%20Davinder%20travelled%20to%20Spain%20and%20Italy%20for%20training%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F470043%2Fabhishek-reddy-left-crore-job-himachal-farm-permaculture-manali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotected%20cultivation.%3C%2Fa%3E%20What%20he%20saw%20there%20shifted%20his%20worldview.%C2%A0%3C%